\text{Verify whether the vector field } \vec{E} = YZ\,\vec{a}_x + XZ\,\vec{a}_y + XY\,\vec{a}_z \text{ is both solenoidal and irrotational?} 
\text{Assertion [A] : Solenoidal and irrotational.} 
\text{Reason [R] : } \nabla \cdot \vec{E} = 0 \text{ and } \nabla \times \vec{E} = 0.

